title: Naked Singularity
description: Naked Singularity is a 2021 American comedy-drama film, directed by Chase Palmer in his directorial debut, from a screenplay by Palmer and David Matthews. It is based upon the 2008 novel of the same name by Sergio De La Pava. It stars John Boyega, Olivia Cooke, Bill Skarsg\u00E5rd, Ed Skrein, Linda Lavin and Tim Blake Nelson.
